Description:
You do not know where they have come from but in front of you there is a group of goblins building a settlement.

The most surprising thing is that the leader of the goblins is a slime and everyone obeys his instructions, the slime sees you and says:

"Hello, I am Rumuri, we are a group of peaceful monsters and we want to build a home in this forest, tonight we will celebrate a banquet and you can stay if you want."
DescriptionAction: You are surprised that a slime can talk to you.
